
IMAPStore philipp@thaler.fyi-remote
Host mail.spacemail.com
Port 993
User philipp@thaler.fyi
PassCmd "pass philipp@thaler.fyi"
AuthMechs LOGIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore philipp@thaler.fyi-local
Flatten .
Path /home/philipp/.local/share/mail/philipp@thaler.fyi/
Inbox /home/philipp/.local/share/mail/philipp@thaler.fyi/INBOX

Channel philipp@thaler.fyi
Expunge Both
Far :philipp@thaler.fyi-remote:
Near :philipp@thaler.fyi-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Near
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile
